:"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of its being quiescent and the preceding letter's being with kesr; the letter preceding it being made movent because it and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"are quiescent after the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"has fallen out; [for by dropping the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"it becomes changed from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoyuwTN","text_ar":"مَخْيُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxowoTN","text_ar":"مَخْوْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] and it is made movent with kesr [and thus changed from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxowoTN","text_ar":"مَخْوْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxiwoTN","text_ar":"مَخِوْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which necessarily becomes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxiyTN","text_ar":"مَخِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] in order to its being known that the letter which has dropped out is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":": some say that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxiyTN","text_ar":"مَخِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the radical, and that the letter thrown out is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in order that the word with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for its medial radical] may be known from that with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [so that it is changed from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoyuwTN","text_ar":"مَخْيُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoyuTN","text_ar":"مَخْيُطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and then to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoyoTN","text_ar":"مَخْيْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and then to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxiyTN","text_ar":"مَخِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] but the former saying is the right, because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a formative augment, and it is not proper that such should be thrown out. (S.) ―         -b2-  Also, the former, (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whole of the exterior"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the belly. (ISh.) ―         -b3-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of passage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L, TA;) a meaning erroneously assigned in the K to ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaATN","text_ar":"خِيَاطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoyaTN","text_ar":"مَخْيَطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and particularly, (tropical:)  of a serpent; (TA;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of creeping along"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a serpent. (K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n11848","headword_ar":"مِخْيَطٌ","root":"xyT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayoTN","text_ar":"خَيْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b2-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaATN","text_ar":"خِيَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxiyTN","text_ar":"مَخِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}